{"tid":1283292,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[富婆] IU在楊平郡購買了30億韓元的住宅","createTime":"2019-07-03T18:23:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-04T03:31:53.000Z","uid":34643,"like":20,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"9f70d1d7c7e30fad68ce5c59aaa707968cfea7c0","tid":1283292,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T18:23:57.000Z","msg":"<ins>190617 IU方面表示:&quot;楊平郡購買了30億韓元的住宅...家人和休息的用途。&quot;</ins><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://dingyue.ws.126.net/VbXRYfcH4SNZnrRgJ79zaUjTnYEw3oihtLgsEkod5Xn7=1552541783634compressflag.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2FVbXRYfcH4SNZnrRgJ79zaUjTnYEw3oihtLgsEkod5Xn7%3D1552541783634compressflag.jpg&h=701c5736&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n歌手兼演員IU去年以30億韓元購買了京畿道楊平的住宅和土地。<br />\n<br />\nIU的經紀公司Kakao M相關人士17日上午對新聞表示:&quot;IU確實購買了位於京畿道楊平郡的住宅。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n接着他解釋說&quot;據我所知,這是爲了在週末或有時間的時候和家人們一起度過而買入的&quot;。<br />\n<br />\n當天,報道說,IU去年年底以30億韓元購買了位於京畿道楊平郡的田園住宅。IU以22億韓元購買了兩層樓規模的楊平田園住宅,之後又以8億韓元購買了周邊6塊土地。<br />\n<br />\n楊平郡不僅有IU,還有演員,歌手等藝人的田園住宅。 據悉,在IU住宅周圍住着80多名藝人。該副董事長補充說,&quot;幾乎沒有投資者,大多數是實際需求者。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n相關韓網評論 請南韓記者離IU的私生活遠一點<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/jmtfvD4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FjmtfvD4.jpg&h=6bb11cb9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n記者到底想做什麼呢？<br />\n<br />\n韓評一面倒的罵記者，這事情為何會變成新聞的素材，毫無意義<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i2.linkoooo.com/1903/20190327212012_6bc7abfc60a8f6ff7369f6b492eb929d_k63s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi2.linkoooo.com%2F1903%2F20190327212012_6bc7abfc60a8f6ff7369f6b492eb929d_k63s.jpg&h=7b78ded2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://k.kakaocdn.net/dn/28wNi/btqtT6E72aV/krW9Q2MO0zK64AZZAhHMMK/img.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fk.kakaocdn.net%2Fdn%2F28wNi%2FbtqtT6E72aV%2FkrW9Q2MO0zK64AZZAhHMMK%2Fimg.jpg&h=0449f9d7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"39402a5b799667b25b89b5f4978f632f00443d77","tid":1283292,"uid":49004,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T18:43:18.000Z","msg":"好想比IU包養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57dc5148736f366ce07fd357ea03592ef1e002a4","tid":1283292,"uid":1086,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T19:17:04.000Z","msg":"屌你老母,<br />\n香港是但一個地鐵上蓋都10M啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3266b3ebaf681f21b96562999cd51dbf1de956e","tid":1283292,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"39402a5b799667b25b89b5f4978f632f00443d77","tid":1283292,"uid":49004,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T18:43:18.000Z","msg":"好想比IU包養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T19:48:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">李知恩圖報(IU包養中)</span>"},{"pid":"4bdf0b2e44148dfd73b26a57a16c8340b59a2507","tid":1283292,"uid":7699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T23:52:25.000Z","msg":"佢買俾我架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c113f1ae34aba20fde33e1901095f51f276713ae","tid":1283292,"uid":135867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T23:57:47.000Z","msg":"二千萬"},{"pid":"e0cffc426f0d2e863638b76649d5748c70718985","tid":1283292,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4bdf0b2e44148dfd73b26a57a16c8340b59a2507","tid":1283292,"uid":7699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T23:52:25.000Z","msg":"佢買俾我架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T01:04:09.000Z","msg":"<img s